            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Hd1e108">Rubrica 11</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De coniectura morum per verba</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>
      ¶ De coniectura morum perverba. Rubrica. 11.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="17"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Rd1e115">SAlomon in prouerb. c. 12.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Qd1e123">
               Do<lb ed="#V" n="18" break="no"/>ctrina noscitur vir.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-d1e129">
               <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Rd1e127">Cronica de nugis philosophorum. c. 2 scilicet de 
               sol<lb ed="#V" n="20" break="no"/>one.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Qd1e133">Solon qui fuit vnus de. vii. 
               sapienti<lb ed="#V" n="21" break="no"/>bus dicebat: verbum imaginem esse operum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-d1e142">
               <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Rd1e143">Aristoteles ethicorum lib. 4. c. 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Qd1e146">
               Unusquis<lb ed="#V" n="23" break="no"/>que qualis est: talia dicit et operatur: et sic viuit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-d1e152">
               <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Rd1e155">Iesus filius sirach in eccl. c. 27.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Qd1e156">Uerbum
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>ostendit excogitatum hominis. Ante sermones
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>non collaudes virum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-d1e164">
               <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Rd1e169">Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum li. 10. e. 8.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="28"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Qd1e168">Iracundi hominis iracundia oratio est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-d1e174">
               <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Rd1e180">Cato. ca. 5. et fi.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Qd1e178">Prospicito cuncta tacitus quod quisque loquatur
        <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>Sermo hominum mores celat: et indicat idem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-d1e186">
               <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Rd1e193">Cassiodorus epistolarum in prohem.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Qd1e190">Oratio 
               dis<lb ed="#V" n="33" break="no"/>par moribus vix potest inueniri.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-d1e196"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Rd1e203">Lib. 5. e. 22.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="34"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Qd1e198">Est quoddam speculum morum agentis oratio: nec
        <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>maius potest esse mentis testimonium quam 
               qua<lb ed="#V" n="36" break="no"/>litas inspecta verborum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-d1e209"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Rd1e217">Li. 6. e. 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Qd1e211">Speculum
        <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>siquidem cordis hominum verba sunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-d1e217">
               <lb ed="#V" n="38"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Rd1e229">Isidorus in sinonima soliloquiorum li. 2. c.
        <lb ed="#V" n="39"/>31</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Qd1e221">Sermo vanus: vane conscientie index est.
        <lb ed="#V" n="40"/>Mores hominis lingua pandit.
        <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>Qualis sermo ostenditur: talis animus comprobatur</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-d1e231">
               <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Rd1e246">Bernardus li. de improbatione vitiorum. c. 5</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="43"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Qd1e235">Ex feda teste fetionus exit odor.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-d1e241">
               <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Rd1e257">Prouerb. vulg.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d48079-Qd1e245">Cotal parola cum tu me 
               di<lb ed="#V" n="45" break="no"/>co: tal cor me fai.<!--153.xml-->
      </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
